title: Walt Disney Treasures - Disneyland
description:
This torrent contains two sets of DVDs about Disneyland from the Walt Disney Treasures series.

The Disneyland, USA set contains various episodes of the Walt Disney anthology series that took place within, or are about, Disneyland. It includes the very first episode from the anthology series.

The Disneyland: Secrets, Stories and Magic set contains other videos about Disneyland.
